==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: permanent wave
<hw>permanent wave</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A wave or curl in
the hair that lasts for months and is made durable by treating the hair
with chemicals when it is curled.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> permanent.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The process of treating the hair with chemicals to
create a <er>permanent wave</er>{1}.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Permanganate</ent>⟦br⟧
